posting_body: ['Ask us about our move-in specials!', 'Enjoy our cozy collection of luxury apartments in Oakland, happily tucked in our little pocket of Temescal.', 'We’re dedicated to bringing you a thoughtful and welcoming sanctuary wrapped in the vibrant surrounds of Temescal.', 'We may be small in numbers (43 total residences), but we’re big in what we bring to the table with our unique floor plan options.', 'That’s our promise, and we want you to hold us to it.', 'Contact us today and schedule a tour to learn more about our wonderful community!', '-Online Rent Payments and Service Request', '-Rooftop Deck with Dining Area and Lounge', '-Oversize Rain Shower Heads', '-Stainless-Steel and Energy Efficient Appliance Package', '-Freeway Access Nearby', '-Dog Run', '-Short Distance to BART and AC Transit', '-Quartz Countertops', '-Garage Parking Available', '-Recycling', '-Bike Racks', '-Controlled Access/Gated', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
